OL,7,FA report into the maternity service at
OL,8,Fthe Royal Sussex County Hospital has
OL,9,Ffound that more work is needed to
OL,10,Fensure it meets the needs of women and
OL,11,Fbabies.
OL,13,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,14,Fcarried out an inspection of the Royal
OL,15,FSussex County Hospital in February,
OL,16,Flooking at both maternity and urgent
OL,17,Fand emergency care services.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/18
