OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FMaternity services at the hospital
OL,8,Fwere upgraded to "requires
OL,9,Fimprovement", having previously been
OL,10,Frated as "inadequate", while emergency
OL,11,Fservices have also been rated as
OL,12,F"requires improvement".
OL,14,FWhile the CQC said there was evidence
OL,15,Fof improvement in maternity services,
OL,16,Fthe inspectors found five breaches of
OL,17,Fregulation on issues including
OL,18,Fcaesarean sections and safeguarding.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/18
