OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FThe University Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust said it has made
OL,9,Fprogress but is under no illusions
OL,10,Fabout the pressures facing the local
OL,11,Fhealth system.
OL,13,FRob Miller and Katie Fowler, whose
OL,14,Fdaughter Abigail died two days after
OL,15,Fbeing born at the Royal Sussex County
OL,16,FHospital, expressed their
OL,17,Fdisappointment at the findings of the
OL,18,Freport.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/18
