OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FAn inquest into Abigail's death found
OL,8,Fthat had Katie been admitted sooner,
OL,9,FAbigail would have survived.
OL,11,FMs Fowler said: "It's been four years
OL,12,Fsince maternity at the Royal Sussex
OL,13,Fwas rated inadequate, nearly four
OL,14,Fyears since Abigail died there, and
OL,15,Fhonestly I thought there would be more
OL,16,Fimprovement by this stage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
