OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"Requires improvement still means that
OL,8,Fthere's still a lot that's going on
OL,9,Fthere, a lot that isn't good about the
OL,10,Fway the service is run and honestly
OL,11,FI'm quite upset really that they
OL,12,Fhaven't managed to get on top of this
OL,13,Fproblem sooner."
OL,15,FMr Miller added: "It's extremely
OL,16,Fpersonal to us. There's a lot in that
OL,17,Freport that still indicates there are
OL,18,Fbig issues that need to be sorted out
OL,19,Fand the steps the have been taken so
OL,20,Ffar seem very small."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/18
