OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FThe CQC also found several concerns in
OL,8,Fthe urgent and emergency care service,
OL,9,Fincluding excessively long waits for
OL,10,Fadmission, instances of patients being
OL,11,Ftreated in corridors and situations
OL,12,Fwhere the dignity and privacy of
OL,13,Fpatients was not protected
OL,15,FThe CQC added that on the day of its
OL,16,Fvisit, eleven people had been in the
OL,17,Femergency department for more than 24
OL,18,Fhours waiting for a bed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
