OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FPatients also told inspectors they
OL,8,Ffelt frustrated and weren't always
OL,9,Fkept informed about their care.
OL,11,FAmanda Williams, CQC deputy director
OL,12,Fof hospitals, secondary and specialist
OL,13,Fcare in Sussex, said: "During our
OL,14,Finspection... Women and people using
OL,15,Fthe service told us staff treated them
OL,16,Fwith compassion and kindness, and we
OL,17,Fobserved strong teamwork between
OL,18,Fdoctors, midwives, and other
OL,19,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
