CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"However, we also found new concerns
OL,8,Faround the effectiveness of the
OL,9,Fservice. The design and environment of
OL,10,Fthe maternity unit didn't fully meet
OL,11,Fthe needs of women, people using the
OL,12,Fservice and their babies.
OL,14,F"There was only one dedicated
OL,15,Fobstetric theatre, which impacted the
OL,16,Fflow of the department.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/18
