OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"The trust ran a pilot in July last
OL,8,Fyear to introduce a second theatre
OL,9,Fpermanently, and staff told us the
OL,10,Fpilot had been successful and well
OL,11,Freceived.
OL,13,F"Despite this, the pilot ended in
OL,14,FAugust that same year, and there was
OL,15,Fstill no permanent solution in place."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/18
