OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,FMs Williams continued: "We found
OL,8,Fseveral concerns in the urgent and
OL,9,Femergency department. Some people were
OL,10,Fbeing cared for in non-clinical areas,
OL,11,Fincluding corridors, which didn't
OL,12,Fprotect their privacy and dignity.
OL,14,F"We were particularly worried about
OL,15,Ftemporary escalation areas that failed
OL,16,Fto support effective care, especially
OL,17,Ffor people whose health was
OL,18,Fdeteriorating.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/18
