OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"Some people told us they felt
OL,8,Ffrustrated and weren't always kept
OL,9,Finformed about their care.
OL,11,F"The department was severely affected
OL,12,Fby poor flow across the hospital,
OL,13,Fleading to delayed ambulance handovers
OL,14,Fand excessively long waits for
OL,15,Fadmission.
OL,17,F"On the day of our visit, 11 people
OL,18,Fhad been in the emergency department
OL,19,Ffor more than 24 hours waiting for a
OL,20,Fbed.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/18
