OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"Senior leaders didn't always take
OL,8,Fsufficient action during this
OL,9,Fovercrowding, as communication about
OL,10,Foperational pressures didn't
OL,11,Fconsistently reach them.
OL,13,F"Staff said they escalated concerns
OL,14,Fbut didn't always get timely responses
OL,15,Fto keep people safe.
OL,17,F"Following our inspection, we made
OL,18,Fclear to the trust where immediate
OL,19,Faction was needed to improve safety in
OL,20,Fthe emergency department and mitigate
OL,21,Fthe risks identified.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/18
