OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"We're meeting regularly with senior
OL,8,Fleaders to monitor progress and make
OL,9,Fsure necessary improvements are made
OL,10,Fand to keep people safe while this
OL,11,Fhappens."
OL,13,FIn response to the CQC's finding on
OL,14,Fits maternity services, Dr Andy Heeps,
OL,15,FChief Executive Officer of University
OL,16,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,17,Fsaid: "I welcome the Care Quality
OL,18,FCommission's recognition of the
OL,19,Fprogress made in our Brighton
OL,20,Fmaternity services.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/18
