OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"We introduced extra theatre capacity
OL,8,Ffor election caesarean sections to
OL,9,Fimprove access and reduce delays, and
OL,10,Fwe strengthened leadership with key
OL,11,Fsenior appointments to ensure services
OL,12,Fare well managed and responsive.
OL,14,F"While the service has moved up a
OL,15,Flevel overall to 'requires
OL,16,Fimprovement', with upgrades in the
OL,17,F'safe' and 'well-led' ratings, we
OL,18,Ftotally accept that we need to go
OL,19,Ffurther.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/18
