OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"We are continually talking with
OL,8,Ffamilies and staff to understand what
OL,9,Fmore we can do to provide the safest,
OL,10,Fmost compassionate care for mothers,
OL,11,Fbabies, and families across Sussex."
OL,13,FIn relation to the Emergency
OL,14,FDepartment, Dr Heeps said: "The
OL,15,Fchallenges highlighted in the Care
OL,16,FQuality Commission's report on our
OL,17,Femergency department are well known,
OL,18,Fand since the inspection in February
OL,19,Fwe have taken significant steps to
OL,20,Faddress them.
OL,26,@sD@dO]vD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/18
