OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"These include opening a new Acute
OL,8,FMedical Unit to help ease pressures,
OL,9,Fmoving patients to other wards at an
OL,10,Fearlier stage where possible, and
OL,11,Fworking closely with partners to
OL,12,Fintroduce new ways of assessing and
OL,13,Fcaring for people outside hospital -
OL,14,Fhelping to reduce the need for
OL,15,Fvulnerable individuals to attend A&E
OL,16,Fin the first place.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/18
