OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1766004462
OL,3,C'More work needed' at maternity
OL,4,Cservice, as bereaved family share
OL,5,C'upset'
OL,7,F"We've made progress, but we are under
OL,8,Fno illusions about the very real
OL,9,Fpressures facing the local health
OL,10,Fsystem. At times, these pressures can
OL,11,Fbe difficult for both patients and
OL,12,Fstaff, particularly in emergency care.
OL,14,F"Longer-term developments, including
OL,15,Fthe #62 million Acute Floor
OL,16,FReconfiguration project, will further
OL,17,Fstrengthen our ability to deliver
OL,18,Fsafe, timely, and compassionate
OL,19,Femergency care for our community."
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@bO]
